WEBVTT

01:35.900 --> 01:40.980
=Love Beyond the Grave=
(Adapted from the novel by Li Qingran)

01:41.260 --> 01:43.980
=Episode 7=

01:52.750 --> 01:53.863
Let me change your dressing.

01:54.390 --> 01:55.230
Only a minor wound.

01:55.750 --> 01:56.860
I don't need tending.

01:58.060 --> 01:58.900
Wan,

01:59.340 --> 02:00.390
go get some rest first.

02:04.220 --> 02:05.140
Then I'll head back.

02:05.910 --> 02:07.190
Stay at Lin Mansion these days

02:07.190 --> 02:08.030
to heal your wounds.

02:08.180 --> 02:09.620
Commandant Xia and I are at camp.

02:09.620 --> 02:10.460
Don't worry.

02:44.230 --> 02:45.230
I've already seen

02:45.230 --> 02:46.270
all of you before.

02:47.420 --> 02:48.740
Even if you're dressed,

02:48.900 --> 02:50.620
it won't restore your honor anyway.

02:51.230 --> 02:52.230
No need to care

02:52.993 --> 02:53.899
about the mortal form.

03:03.790 --> 03:05.550
Your Grace, I didn't know you'd come.

03:05.990 --> 03:06.830
Sorry.

03:11.990 --> 03:13.510
When did you, Meng Wan,

03:14.790 --> 03:15.950
and Xia Qingsheng first meet?

03:19.620 --> 03:21.180
After I returned to Nandu from Daizhou,

03:21.950 --> 03:23.550
we studied under Academician Yang.

03:24.860 --> 03:25.720
That was all

03:25.720 --> 03:26.790
after you turned 18.

03:27.700 --> 03:29.510
How is it that every friend

03:29.790 --> 03:30.630
and teacher you name

03:31.020 --> 03:32.270
came into your life after that?

03:33.390 --> 03:34.950
What were you doing before you were 18?

03:35.830 --> 03:37.990
The master blinded by a goose

03:38.390 --> 03:39.270
was your teacher

03:39.270 --> 03:40.350
before 18, wasn't he?

03:41.110 --> 03:42.420
Was the amnesiac Han Lingqiu

03:43.230 --> 03:44.790
your friend before you were 18?

03:53.700 --> 03:54.540
My master

03:55.550 --> 03:56.900
was from before I turned 18,

03:57.790 --> 03:58.670
but Han was not.

03:59.740 --> 04:01.020
I had no friends before I was 18.

04:10.550 --> 04:11.830
Who are you, really?

04:12.020 --> 04:12.860
Duan Xu.

04:15.900 --> 04:18.260
Duan Shunxi.

04:25.550 --> 04:26.550
Your Grace,

04:27.470 --> 04:28.310
please…

04:28.590 --> 04:29.670
Please show mercy.

04:35.940 --> 04:37.260
Your martial arts are superb.

04:38.180 --> 04:39.420
Why not struggle?

04:40.230 --> 04:41.070
Why not resist?

04:43.230 --> 04:44.710
Before absolute power,

04:46.860 --> 04:47.990
skill means nothing.

04:50.300 --> 04:51.420
I can't defeat you.

04:53.060 --> 04:54.060
Other than begging,

04:54.060 --> 04:54.910
I have no other way.

05:01.060 --> 05:02.710
What if I don't spare you?

05:07.030 --> 05:07.940
You wish

05:09.300 --> 05:11.030
to keep my skull, right?

05:12.260 --> 05:13.790
When I reach 50,

05:14.820 --> 05:16.300
my skull will look even finer.

05:17.550 --> 05:18.860
Why not wait a while

05:20.110 --> 05:21.180
until I turn 50

05:21.180 --> 05:22.020
and devour me then?

05:24.030 --> 05:25.230
I won't harm you.

05:35.030 --> 05:36.670
I want to make a deal with you.

05:56.110 --> 05:57.470
I'm listening.

05:58.940 --> 06:00.380
The deal is simple.

06:01.440 --> 06:02.300
I will grant

06:02.300 --> 06:03.380
one of your wishes.

06:04.380 --> 06:05.470
In return,

06:05.940 --> 06:07.740
you will lend me your five senses.

06:08.990 --> 06:10.060
One wish,

06:10.590 --> 06:11.590
one sense.

06:13.470 --> 06:14.310
For ten days.

06:20.030 --> 06:21.030
During those ten days,

06:22.420 --> 06:23.790
I will lose that sense.

06:24.550 --> 06:25.390
That's right.

06:26.350 --> 06:27.500
This is the limit

06:27.500 --> 06:28.820
a mortal body can bear.

06:30.470 --> 06:31.710
After ten days,

06:32.180 --> 06:33.260
I will return your senses

06:33.260 --> 06:34.100
to you.

06:34.940 --> 06:36.180
Once you recover,

06:36.710 --> 06:38.470
we begin the next exchange.

06:39.590 --> 06:40.670
That means

06:41.590 --> 06:43.300
you may ask many wishes of me,

06:44.670 --> 06:46.230
but wishes have their limits.

06:46.940 --> 06:48.306
They can't alter the mortal world.

06:49.300 --> 06:50.140
For example,

06:51.350 --> 06:52.620
you may wish for me

06:52.990 --> 06:54.590
to save your life in battle,

06:55.300 --> 06:56.470
but you may not wish

06:56.740 --> 06:58.500
for me to win the war for you.

07:06.260 --> 07:07.500
What if I do not agree?

07:37.180 --> 07:38.500
We have come this far already.

07:38.990 --> 07:40.590
You no longer get to refuse.

07:53.910 --> 07:55.500
Must we speak in this position?

08:01.740 --> 08:02.670
What is wrong with it?

08:05.710 --> 08:08.180
You are not light;

08:09.590 --> 08:10.430
you are quite cold.

08:12.060 --> 08:12.900
General,

08:13.820 --> 08:16.180
I fetched this medicine

08:17.620 --> 08:18.460
for you.

08:21.820 --> 08:22.660
I...

08:58.310 --> 08:59.150
Commandant Xia.

09:03.710 --> 09:04.550
Where are you going?

09:05.230 --> 09:06.070
I made some food.

09:06.070 --> 09:06.920
I'm taking it to Xu.

09:08.710 --> 09:10.230
I just saw the General.

09:10.700 --> 09:11.540
He's not hungry.

09:11.550 --> 09:12.500
No need for this.

09:13.830 --> 09:15.430
And you would know if he is hungry?

09:15.950 --> 09:16.790
Xu has gone all day

09:16.800 --> 09:17.900
without one hot bite.

09:18.110 --> 09:19.430
Move. Or it'll go cold soon.

09:21.900 --> 09:23.270
What are you doing? Xia...

09:23.780 --> 09:24.620
This wasn't for you.

09:33.500 --> 09:34.430
Fine.

09:34.430 --> 09:35.270
Xia Qingsheng,

09:35.860 --> 09:36.700
just you wait.

09:50.110 --> 09:50.950
Miss He,

09:52.370 --> 09:53.230
you and the General

09:53.230 --> 09:54.470
have really ruined me.

09:59.710 --> 10:00.590
Your Grace,

10:01.430 --> 10:03.016
is this your first trade for the senses?

10:05.990 --> 10:07.020
It's a trifling matter.

10:07.710 --> 10:08.950
I paid it no mind.

10:12.780 --> 10:13.830
So, you admit it.

10:15.230 --> 10:16.660
You came near me

10:16.660 --> 10:17.540
for the Deliverance.

10:18.590 --> 10:19.430
I believe

10:19.590 --> 10:20.830
the one who can trade with you

10:21.660 --> 10:22.990
must be the Deliverance's master.

10:25.710 --> 10:26.683
When the old man gave me

10:26.950 --> 10:27.950
the sword, he said

10:28.380 --> 10:29.220
the Deliverance

10:29.350 --> 10:30.470
had no master for 300 years.

10:31.430 --> 10:32.270
By that reckoning,

10:32.590 --> 10:33.740
I am the fated one

10:34.260 --> 10:35.350
you waited

10:35.350 --> 10:36.190
for 300 years for.

10:36.710 --> 10:38.230
Just a pastime on my rest day.

10:38.500 --> 10:39.590
Don't flatter yourself.

10:39.590 --> 10:40.990
How many years have you lived

10:41.660 --> 10:42.740
without the five senses?

10:43.230 --> 10:44.710
We don't need such things.

10:45.540 --> 10:46.830
What a pity, then.

10:47.900 --> 10:48.740
Nothing to pity.

10:49.690 --> 10:50.752
Those are only the cravings

10:50.763 --> 10:52.020
of you mortals.

10:54.140 --> 10:55.380
I mean myself.

10:56.470 --> 10:57.380
I've thought about it,

10:57.900 --> 10:58.740
yet I can't think

10:58.740 --> 10:59.950
of a single wish.

11:01.830 --> 11:02.710
Your Grace,

11:04.900 --> 11:05.950
I never make wishes.

11:09.380 --> 11:10.260
For hundreds of years,

11:11.950 --> 11:13.780
I've dealt with countless mortals,

11:14.230 --> 11:15.260
yet never have I heard one

11:15.260 --> 11:16.260
truly say,

11:16.710 --> 11:17.550
"No need."

11:17.900 --> 11:19.070
"I have lived well"

11:19.590 --> 11:20.620
"and can rest in peace."

11:20.620 --> 11:21.860
"I want nothing at all."

11:22.260 --> 11:23.260
No exception.

11:24.590 --> 11:25.740
Let alone you.

11:31.500 --> 11:32.500
I never ask others

11:34.470 --> 11:35.950
to grant my desires.

11:39.350 --> 11:40.860
Had I not saved you today,

11:41.430 --> 11:43.070
you'd have fallen to the Chong troops.

11:43.950 --> 11:45.500
On the battlefield, life hangs thin.

11:46.350 --> 11:47.860
Are you certain that without my aid,

11:48.380 --> 11:49.990
you could escape death every time?

11:51.310 --> 11:52.150
No matter what,

11:54.260 --> 11:55.620
thank you for today.

12:02.540 --> 12:03.590
General,

12:04.470 --> 12:06.070
you are too young.

12:06.620 --> 12:08.660
You must know fate is ever-shifting,

12:09.230 --> 12:10.620
beyond any mortal's grasp.

12:11.950 --> 12:12.990
Fate is ever-shifting,

12:14.380 --> 12:15.500
but so am I.

12:19.780 --> 12:20.660
Was the look yesterday

12:21.020 --> 12:22.230
your true form?

12:23.110 --> 12:24.430
I remember your robes

12:24.590 --> 12:25.543
were exquisitely ornate,

12:26.020 --> 12:26.860
unlike the mortals'.

12:27.230 --> 12:28.780
If you're curious,

12:29.380 --> 12:31.140
go dig up a few tombs
from 400 years ago.

12:31.140 --> 12:32.070
You'll see enough.

12:32.660 --> 12:33.900
So, you're 400 years old?

13:17.020 --> 13:17.860
You're reluctant

13:17.860 --> 13:19.110
to see me go, right?

13:19.710 --> 13:20.860
So, I won't leave.

13:23.470 --> 13:24.950
I'll sleep here tonight.

13:28.620 --> 13:29.590
Come on, then.

13:33.590 --> 13:34.830
I'll be unable

13:35.070 --> 13:36.070
to sleep again.

13:44.660 --> 13:45.620
Shall I share my pillow

13:45.620 --> 13:46.460
with you?

13:47.230 --> 13:48.310
In the dead of night,

13:48.310 --> 13:50.310
with a spirit lying in your bed,

13:50.990 --> 13:52.110
aren't you afraid?

13:53.070 --> 13:55.020
I do feed on people, you know.

14:00.590 --> 14:01.540
We fight over land,

14:02.056 --> 14:03.349
till the dead blanket the fields.

14:04.900 --> 14:05.740
We fight over cities,

14:06.590 --> 14:07.850
till the dead fill every street.

14:08.540 --> 14:10.660
We seize land at the cost of the living.

14:12.070 --> 14:12.950
By that measure,

14:14.470 --> 14:15.470
we're of the same trade.

14:39.020 --> 14:40.350
And you said you couldn't sleep.

14:41.260 --> 14:42.260
Foxy,

14:42.950 --> 14:44.350
not a word from you is true.

14:49.430 --> 14:50.780
But looking at you now,

14:51.430 --> 14:52.780
I don't think you're so clever.

14:54.740 --> 14:55.950
More like a rabbit.

15:19.660 --> 15:20.500
Han.

15:23.950 --> 15:24.790
Han,

15:25.020 --> 15:26.500
what on earth is going on?

15:27.470 --> 15:28.620
The General locked me up.

15:29.500 --> 15:30.660
I don't know what's going on.

15:33.950 --> 15:34.790
Han,

15:35.110 --> 15:35.950
I know.

15:36.140 --> 15:37.540
You must be innocent.

15:37.860 --> 15:38.740
If it's hard for you

15:38.740 --> 15:40.500
to say certain things,

15:40.500 --> 15:41.350
tell me instead.

15:41.350 --> 15:42.950
I'll plead with the General.

15:43.780 --> 15:44.980
The innocent need no defense.

15:45.470 --> 15:46.310
I trust the General.

15:47.230 --> 15:48.470
He will clear my name.

15:53.140 --> 15:53.980
Han,

15:54.350 --> 15:55.190
rest easy.

15:55.740 --> 15:57.310
With me here,

15:57.900 --> 15:59.230
I won't let you suffer this wrong.

16:14.860 --> 16:15.700
Xiaoxiao,

16:16.230 --> 16:17.110
yesterday, the General

16:17.120 --> 16:17.970
brought grain back

16:17.990 --> 16:19.160
and distributed it again.

16:19.860 --> 16:21.740
We're not short of food here.

16:24.500 --> 16:25.740
Best to be prepared.

16:27.110 --> 16:28.070
But Xiaoxiao,

16:28.230 --> 16:29.110
don't worry.

16:29.110 --> 16:30.380
Lin told me

16:30.900 --> 16:32.620
that as long as we stay here,

16:32.830 --> 16:34.310
we will not go short of food.

16:34.540 --> 16:35.380
You seem

16:35.380 --> 16:36.500
to be close to everyone.

16:37.540 --> 16:38.380
You like him?

16:39.780 --> 16:40.780
Of course.

16:41.900 --> 16:42.740
Lin is

16:42.900 --> 16:44.310
kind to everyone.

16:44.710 --> 16:46.310
He also helped the General a lot,

16:46.710 --> 16:47.990
procuring and distributing grain.

16:48.350 --> 16:49.430
Besides the General,

16:49.430 --> 16:50.830
he is everyone's hero too.

16:52.590 --> 16:53.430
Xiaoxiao,

16:54.070 --> 16:55.710
you always eat so little.

16:56.860 --> 16:58.950
I know you can't bear to eat more,

16:59.430 --> 17:01.260
because you save the best for me.

17:02.380 --> 17:04.540
You even fainted from hunger before.

17:06.150 --> 17:07.260
But Xiaoxiao,

17:07.820 --> 17:09.580
we have enough grain now.

17:09.910 --> 17:11.470
You needn't starve yourself anymore.

17:11.470 --> 17:12.310
Young Master.

17:13.150 --> 17:14.780
Young Master, this is bad.

17:14.910 --> 17:16.412
(Ultimate Joy)
The master was caught

17:16.423 --> 17:17.523
and brought below the city.

17:17.670 --> 17:18.510
Young Master.

17:19.190 --> 17:20.030
Let's go.

17:21.230 --> 17:22.070
Xiaoxiao,

17:22.870 --> 17:23.870
do you think Lin

17:23.870 --> 17:24.710
might be in danger?

17:25.190 --> 17:26.030
You want to go see?

17:41.100 --> 17:41.940
Uncle.

17:42.630 --> 17:43.580
- Uncle.
- Mr. Lin.

17:43.580 --> 17:44.900
- Mr. Lin.
- Uncle.

17:46.710 --> 17:47.630
Master Lin.

17:48.780 --> 17:49.910
Talk with the ones

17:49.910 --> 17:50.990
on the wall.

17:51.780 --> 17:52.710
They are

17:52.710 --> 17:53.740
your family.

17:56.260 --> 17:59.300
(Lin Huaide, main branch)

17:59.300 --> 18:00.140
Jun.

18:01.500 --> 18:02.340
I'm here.

18:03.100 --> 18:04.390
Have you received the provisions?

18:05.230 --> 18:06.070
They're here.

18:08.100 --> 18:09.190
Is it enough?

18:10.430 --> 18:11.270
Yes.

18:12.670 --> 18:13.710
Thanks, Mr. Lin.

18:19.390 --> 18:20.230
Jun.

18:21.740 --> 18:22.740
Your grandfather

18:23.670 --> 18:25.230
was once a general of Great Liang.

18:26.870 --> 18:28.780
He fell in Yunzhou and never returned.

18:30.100 --> 18:31.020
Your grandmother

18:32.950 --> 18:34.670
would not flee south
of the Guanhe River.

18:36.950 --> 18:37.790
Because of that,

18:38.390 --> 18:39.780
your father was born.

18:40.100 --> 18:41.580
He stayed in Shuozhou

18:42.500 --> 18:44.230
and built up this family estate.

18:46.190 --> 18:47.100
All these years,

18:47.710 --> 18:49.630
we've bowed to the Chong people.

18:50.390 --> 18:51.470
But you must remember

18:51.950 --> 18:52.790
whose hands

18:53.190 --> 18:54.710
claimed your forebears.

18:55.870 --> 18:56.990
Your grandmother once said,

18:58.100 --> 18:59.260
"If one day"

18:59.950 --> 19:00.790
"Great Liang"

19:01.100 --> 19:03.230
"crosses the Guanhe River
to reclaim the land,"

19:03.870 --> 19:06.150
"though we're merchants,"

19:06.300 --> 19:07.740
"we will give all our strength"

19:08.100 --> 19:09.540
"and never shrink from death."

19:09.540 --> 19:10.380
No!

19:15.470 --> 19:17.100
Jun, listen carefully.

19:18.870 --> 19:21.630
Hold on at all costs.

19:23.150 --> 19:24.340
I came to see you today

19:25.100 --> 19:26.540
to tell you this:

19:27.670 --> 19:28.510
I'm going

19:29.870 --> 19:32.020
to answer to your grandfather.

19:33.500 --> 19:34.710
I will tell him

19:35.540 --> 19:37.780
our clan didn't fail him.

19:39.060 --> 19:39.990
Jun,

19:40.820 --> 19:42.670
you didn't fail him.

19:43.710 --> 19:44.950
One day, surely,

19:46.500 --> 19:48.060
the land will return,

19:55.990 --> 19:57.820
bringing back the golden age.

19:59.990 --> 20:01.060
No!

20:18.780 --> 20:19.620
Kill them.

20:46.150 --> 20:47.020
My father

20:47.580 --> 20:49.630
was slain the same way.

20:50.780 --> 20:51.990
He was unarmed,

20:52.780 --> 20:54.710
cut down like livestock.

21:04.430 --> 21:05.470
General Duan,

21:06.390 --> 21:09.500
was it worth it to trade

21:09.950 --> 21:11.670
23 lives of the Lin clan

21:12.780 --> 21:13.870
for these carts of grain?

21:15.740 --> 21:16.780
Soon, I will take

21:16.780 --> 21:18.340
your head

21:18.820 --> 21:20.540
to console the 23 souls

21:20.540 --> 21:21.470
of the Lin clan above.

21:32.670 --> 21:33.510
Withdraw the troops.

21:33.950 --> 21:34.790
Yes.

22:24.660 --> 22:30.940
(Chongde Chamber)

22:38.870 --> 22:39.710
Young Master,

22:40.390 --> 22:41.870
you've eaten nothing

22:42.060 --> 22:42.990
since yesterday.

22:43.470 --> 22:44.820
The dead can't return.

22:44.900 --> 22:46.226
(Memorial Tablet of Master Huaide)

22:46.237 --> 22:47.190
Master Huaide

22:48.020 --> 22:49.630
would not wish to see this.

22:53.700 --> 22:57.740
(Memorial)

23:17.580 --> 23:18.420
Mr. Lin,

23:20.950 --> 23:21.950
my condolences.

23:21.950 --> 23:24.220
(Memorial Tablet of Master Huaide)

23:24.670 --> 23:25.870
Shuozhou is in grave peril now.

23:27.990 --> 23:29.300
I still need your support.

23:30.470 --> 23:31.710
For the sake of the whole city,

23:32.390 --> 23:33.870
you must pull yourself together soon.

23:35.670 --> 23:36.510
Mr. Lin,

23:37.190 --> 23:38.300
I've failed the Lin clan.

23:43.910 --> 23:45.430
General, do not blame yourself.

23:48.300 --> 23:49.630
All men must die one day.

23:52.500 --> 23:53.430
Uncle

23:55.580 --> 23:57.710
was only betrayed by traitors.

23:59.910 --> 24:00.750
Please rest assured.

24:02.670 --> 24:03.670
I've sent men to recover

24:03.670 --> 24:05.020
all the remains

24:05.910 --> 24:07.020
for burial.

24:23.100 --> 24:24.630
I heard your father died young.

24:27.990 --> 24:29.580
Your uncle cared for you

24:32.740 --> 24:34.020
as if he were your own father.

24:37.340 --> 24:38.820
I know the Lin clan has suffered,

24:40.710 --> 24:41.710
and your heart is heavy.

24:42.910 --> 24:44.190
But right now,

24:44.190 --> 24:45.060
I need your help.

24:47.710 --> 24:48.550
Please agree.

24:50.340 --> 24:51.230
What is it?

24:51.710 --> 24:53.340
It concerns the spy who tipped off

24:54.340 --> 24:55.230
the Chong Army

24:55.230 --> 24:56.390
and got your uncle killed.

24:57.630 --> 24:58.950
But I heard

24:59.740 --> 25:01.260
you've had Captain Han…

25:01.260 --> 25:02.150
I've locked up

25:02.150 --> 25:02.990
Han Lingqiu.

25:04.020 --> 25:05.060
Han Lingqiu

25:05.060 --> 25:06.190
is from North Chong.

25:06.910 --> 25:08.060
He claims he lost his memory,

25:09.710 --> 25:10.870
but too much does not add up.

25:13.630 --> 25:14.470
He lost his memory?

25:15.390 --> 25:16.260
His martial arts style

25:16.260 --> 25:17.470
resembles the Chong people's.

25:19.540 --> 25:20.380
I suspect

25:21.910 --> 25:23.540
he is a spy sent by the Chong Army.

25:24.670 --> 25:25.910
I wish to hold a martial contest

25:27.540 --> 25:28.780
to test his true skills.

25:29.300 --> 25:30.300
I heard you're also

25:31.710 --> 25:32.990
fond of martial arts

25:34.500 --> 25:36.390
and have several skilled guests at home.

25:37.230 --> 25:38.190
May I ask them

25:38.190 --> 25:39.030
to come as well

25:39.670 --> 25:40.950
and face Han Lingqiu in a match?

25:42.390 --> 25:43.230
General,

25:44.430 --> 25:45.540
I am but a humble merchant.

25:47.470 --> 25:48.470
Why entrust the contest

25:49.710 --> 25:51.190
to me?

25:57.670 --> 25:58.870
The Lin clan is loyal.

26:00.390 --> 26:01.670
In the whole army now,

26:02.150 --> 26:03.300
the one I trust most

26:06.260 --> 26:07.470
is only you.

26:14.500 --> 26:15.430
Leave it to me.

26:25.060 --> 26:26.390
The General wants me to fight?

26:26.910 --> 26:27.820
I must win,

26:28.230 --> 26:29.500
yet preserve my strength,

26:30.190 --> 26:31.870
and not reveal it unless forced.

26:32.150 --> 26:32.990
Why?

26:33.580 --> 26:35.260
The General's order is just that.

26:35.710 --> 26:36.820
Are you willing to obey?

26:41.620 --> 26:49.260
(Zhang Mansion)

27:00.470 --> 27:01.310
Are you there?

27:07.390 --> 27:08.300
You've arranged

27:08.300 --> 27:09.340
everything already.

27:12.190 --> 27:13.030
So, you knew it all?

27:14.670 --> 27:16.060
I had guessed most of it.

27:18.820 --> 27:19.950
When this round is over,

27:21.230 --> 27:22.580
we'll see how much you can guess.

27:24.780 --> 27:26.190
You scramble for power and gain

27:26.190 --> 27:27.950
with the same old routine.

27:28.820 --> 27:30.060
I am long tired of watching it.

27:34.580 --> 27:35.540
Tomorrow's show

27:36.300 --> 27:37.670
is more than a hunt for spies.

27:39.300 --> 27:40.710
Your Grace, do be patient,

27:40.877 --> 27:42.037
and watch until the very end.

27:43.710 --> 27:45.100
I will not disappoint you.

27:46.670 --> 27:47.910
Then I'll wait and see.

27:49.870 --> 27:51.260
Do not let me down.

28:05.780 --> 28:09.060
(Liang)

28:21.230 --> 28:22.910
The martial contest begins.

28:23.580 --> 28:25.300
Contestants, enter the arena.

28:34.780 --> 28:36.580
(Wu Junyi, Han Lingqiu)

28:46.670 --> 28:49.150
Captain Han Lingqiu wins.

28:49.150 --> 28:50.060
(Sun Xiu, Han Lingqiu)

28:50.060 --> 28:50.900
(Liang)

29:04.670 --> 29:06.710
Next contestant, enter the arena.

29:09.860 --> 29:11.540
(Ge Tian, Han Lingqiu)

29:15.100 --> 29:16.199
(Zhou Yi'ang, Han Lingqiu)

29:17.220 --> 29:18.162
(Wang Shuo, Han Lingqiu)

29:18.173 --> 29:20.223
Next contestant, enter the arena.

29:21.860 --> 29:23.180
(Lin Mo, Han Lingqiu)

29:25.780 --> 29:26.715
(Han Sheng, Han Lingqiu)

29:26.726 --> 29:28.870
Captain Han Lingqiu wins.

29:35.400 --> 29:36.260
Han,

29:36.260 --> 29:37.100
make your move.

29:38.390 --> 29:39.230
General,

29:39.710 --> 29:40.550
if this keeps up,

29:41.150 --> 29:42.870
we won't see Captain Han's skill.

29:46.060 --> 29:47.300
I've heard that there is

29:48.100 --> 29:49.230
a blindfolded contest

29:49.230 --> 29:50.070
in the Jianghu.

29:50.340 --> 29:52.150
Both sides must judge the position

29:52.150 --> 29:53.156
by the sound of the wind.

29:53.340 --> 29:55.060
It best shows one's martial arts.

30:04.670 --> 30:05.510
Very well.

30:05.950 --> 30:06.790
Anyway,

30:06.790 --> 30:07.910
no winner is clear now.

30:08.630 --> 30:09.470
Let's do it.

30:09.470 --> 30:11.470
Captain Han Lingqiu wins.

30:11.470 --> 30:12.310
Steward,

30:13.300 --> 30:14.500
prepare cloth for blindfolds.

30:14.710 --> 30:15.550
Yes.

30:18.020 --> 30:19.340
The match is suspended.

31:52.300 --> 31:54.230
Captain Han Lingqiu wins.

31:54.230 --> 31:55.740
Han is that skilled?

31:56.140 --> 31:56.990
What a surprise.

31:56.990 --> 31:57.910
How is it that I

31:57.910 --> 31:58.950
never knew this before?

32:08.820 --> 32:09.660
Everyone,

32:10.390 --> 32:11.990
during our time in Shuozhou,

32:14.670 --> 32:15.820
Miss He's carriage

32:15.820 --> 32:16.780
was attacked,

32:18.630 --> 32:20.020
and the provisions were burned.

32:21.780 --> 32:22.746
While seizing the grain,

32:24.580 --> 32:25.430
we ran into an ambush,

32:26.870 --> 32:28.390
and Master Huaide was betrayed.

32:30.100 --> 32:31.950
All these incidents point to one thing:

32:32.540 --> 32:33.710
There is a Chong spy

32:35.020 --> 32:36.470
among us.

32:36.990 --> 32:38.820
Could it really be Captain Han?

32:39.190 --> 32:40.340
I never knew his skills

32:40.340 --> 32:41.190
were this formidable.

32:42.670 --> 32:43.510
Only today

32:45.340 --> 32:46.540
have I finally confirmed

32:46.910 --> 32:48.060
who that spy truly is.

32:49.540 --> 32:50.380
Who is it?

32:51.670 --> 32:52.510
What is going on?

32:53.300 --> 32:54.300
It can't be Captain Han.

32:54.540 --> 32:55.380
Captain Han?

33:06.910 --> 33:07.750
Mr. Lin,

33:08.990 --> 33:09.830
what do you say?

33:13.910 --> 33:14.990
Perhaps I should ask you

33:16.150 --> 33:17.820
where you've hidden

33:18.230 --> 33:19.350
the real Lin Jun

33:19.361 --> 33:20.634
since we entered the inner city?

33:20.910 --> 33:22.540
Is this not Lin Jun, Mr. Lin?

33:22.540 --> 33:23.380
Yes.

33:25.780 --> 33:26.620
What does that mean?

33:31.250 --> 33:32.150
What does that mean?

33:32.150 --> 33:32.990
General,

33:33.470 --> 33:34.500
what do you mean by that?

33:35.950 --> 33:37.260
You suspect I'm a spy?

33:37.540 --> 33:38.380
It's not suspicion.

33:39.260 --> 33:40.150
I'm certain.

33:41.300 --> 33:42.140
Mr. Lin,

33:42.340 --> 33:43.740
may I borrow a carriage?

33:44.150 --> 33:45.020
You honor me, General.

33:45.630 --> 33:46.710
It's a small matter.

33:47.190 --> 33:48.710
Miss He's carriage was attacked.

33:49.470 --> 33:50.710
Han Lingqiu was riding with her.

33:51.150 --> 33:52.630
But the carriage was yours.

33:53.150 --> 33:53.990
General Duan,

33:54.150 --> 33:55.580
may I ease the Tabai Army's burden?

33:56.670 --> 33:57.630
I'll send half my men

33:58.190 --> 33:59.230
to guard the granary.

33:59.470 --> 34:00.540
Thank you, Mr. Lin.

34:01.260 --> 34:02.150
You know

34:02.740 --> 34:03.580
the granary defenses,

34:04.100 --> 34:05.630
the time of the grain raid,

34:06.260 --> 34:07.500
and letters from Master Huaide.

34:08.310 --> 34:09.870
When the Chong people send grain here,

34:10.710 --> 34:11.580
they must pass through

34:11.580 --> 34:12.830
several northern cities.

34:13.790 --> 34:15.500
Our clan has kin in the north.

34:16.220 --> 34:17.500
I sent carrier pigeons to them

34:17.990 --> 34:19.500
to track the grain convoy.

34:21.660 --> 34:23.220
And what does that prove?

34:31.020 --> 34:32.060
I truly did not know

34:32.990 --> 34:34.470
the All-Knowing's Blindfolded Trial

34:35.100 --> 34:36.500
was a rule of jianghu.

34:40.060 --> 34:41.020
Master Fifteen.

34:44.700 --> 34:45.540
Don't come over.

34:45.830 --> 34:46.670
Or I'll end him.

34:48.100 --> 34:49.020
Lin,

34:49.350 --> 34:51.270
I always took you for a real man.

34:51.270 --> 34:52.270
Your uncle

34:52.270 --> 34:53.750
met a grim end below the city wall.

34:54.280 --> 34:55.140
I even felt

34:55.140 --> 34:56.500
I had wronged the Lin clan.

34:56.500 --> 34:57.390
Who would've thought

34:57.950 --> 35:00.060
you were the one who sold him out?

35:00.060 --> 35:01.310
He isn't Lin Jun.

35:02.180 --> 35:03.140
He was only in disguise.

35:03.620 --> 35:04.580
So, the man he sold out

35:04.830 --> 35:05.910
wasn't his own uncle.

35:06.220 --> 35:07.060
That's right.

35:07.750 --> 35:09.060
I am the real Lin Jun.

35:11.580 --> 35:12.620
He seized me

35:13.830 --> 35:15.180
and copied my every move.

35:15.830 --> 35:17.220
He deceived every one of you.

35:17.500 --> 35:18.540
Perfect timing.

35:21.380 --> 35:22.220
I had thought

35:22.220 --> 35:23.540
Lin was a good man.

35:25.910 --> 35:27.350
But I saw him yesterday.

35:28.060 --> 35:28.900
Lin…

35:46.950 --> 35:48.020
I told Xiaoxiao

35:48.020 --> 35:48.860
about this matter.

35:49.100 --> 35:50.270
She told me

35:50.870 --> 35:52.540
to bring the real Lin here today.

35:52.950 --> 35:54.060
You cur!

35:54.580 --> 35:55.830
How dare you deceive us!

35:56.270 --> 35:57.580
You are not leaving today.

35:58.540 --> 35:59.500
You've lost your memory?

35:59.750 --> 36:01.220
What does it have

36:01.390 --> 36:02.470
to do with you?

36:02.700 --> 36:03.540
Without your memory,

36:03.910 --> 36:04.910
you'd be forgivable.

36:06.390 --> 36:07.990
You should be my 17th junior brother.

36:08.390 --> 36:09.696
Come back with me to see Mentor.

36:09.950 --> 36:11.100
Stop talking nonsense.

36:12.100 --> 36:13.020
I am Han Lingqiu,

36:13.660 --> 36:15.390
Captain of Great Liang's Tabai Army.

36:16.180 --> 36:17.660
That's my only identity.

36:18.540 --> 36:19.380
Even if I die,

36:19.390 --> 36:20.470
I'll never go with you.

36:20.790 --> 36:21.990
You were once

36:21.990 --> 36:23.100
Mentor's favorite.

36:23.620 --> 36:25.140
Now, you can't tell right from wrong.

36:26.580 --> 36:28.310
Even Captain Han ignores you now.

36:29.140 --> 36:30.270
Surrender without a fight.

36:30.660 --> 36:31.500
Fool.

36:31.660 --> 36:32.870
As long as I have you,

36:33.750 --> 36:34.910
they won't dare make a move.

36:36.700 --> 36:37.540
Get a horse for me.

36:38.390 --> 36:39.230
I'm leaving the city.

36:43.060 --> 36:44.180
Follow my orders.

36:45.990 --> 36:46.830
Get him a horse.

36:49.020 --> 36:49.860
Let him leave.

37:20.720 --> 37:26.050
♪Between black and white,
ripples crossed♪

37:26.380 --> 37:30.630
♪Light encountered shadow♪

37:31.990 --> 37:37.360
♪It pierced the darkness and the time♪

37:37.660 --> 37:42.260
♪The unbreakable fate♪

37:43.350 --> 37:45.190
♪Suddenly cracked♪

37:57.400 --> 38:02.840
♪Between black and white,
ripples crossed♪

38:03.020 --> 38:07.350
♪Light encountered shadow♪

38:08.720 --> 38:14.110
♪It pierced the darkness and the time♪

38:14.340 --> 38:18.280
♪The unbreakable fate♪

38:20.050 --> 38:21.940
♪Suddenly cracked♪

38:24.600 --> 38:27.760
♪Listen, all sounds are roaring♪

38:27.760 --> 38:30.290
♪As cold ice turns into tides♪

38:30.290 --> 38:35.810
♪A century's loneliness melts dreams♪

38:35.810 --> 38:39.050
♪Following fate's guidance♪

38:39.050 --> 38:43.910
♪By fate, our moments were exchanged♪

38:44.250 --> 38:47.270
♪The heart wakes up all of a sudden♪

38:47.270 --> 38:50.090
♪Watch fireworks fall like stars♪

38:50.350 --> 38:52.880
♪This bond is tangled into a thread♪

38:52.880 --> 38:58.300
♪Worldly reflections fade into mist♪

38:58.470 --> 39:01.540
♪Borrowing one fleeting heartbeat♪

39:01.700 --> 39:06.600
♪You drew me into mortal dust,
till I'm enamored with its charms♪

39:06.810 --> 39:10.280
♪The heart wakes up all of a sudden♪
